{"tid":1781453,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"胖胖跳兔仔舞 !","createTime":"2019-12-13T07:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T10:08:07.000Z","uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c15acf53825bf799285fe5677bd3416d268ba48e","tid":1781453,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6rZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=227cf5ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們，令牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !"},{"pid":"791f616fba0907a676059a70abdfe86693713aef","tid":1781453,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"收皮啦白卡"},{"pid":"548de037f882976de7bb374175d25400be303abf","tid":1781453,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}